data.title: Fairytales, Folklore, & Fables: Keywords & Searching Tips
data.meta_description: Dongeng - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides a summary of resources for fairytales, folklore, and fables available at the Greenwood Public Library. It includes online search tips, print and multimedia materials such as books and films, and suggested search terms. The print and multimedia materials are located at the Greenwood Public Library and were identified using the library catalog. Electronic resources and websites were found through online searches.
